# libm.so - Android Math Library Stub
# Wired up in DynLink but not actively used yet
#
# Key symbols:
#   sin, cos, tan, sqrt, pow, exp, log, log10
#   floor, ceil, round, fabs, fmod
#   sinf, cosf, sqrtf (single-precision variants)
#
# Notes:
#   - Most math functions are implemented in software on ARM64
#   - SIMD/FP instructions (FADD, FMUL, etc.) handle the actual computation
#   - AVX2 backend translates these to x86_64 equivalents
